Interface IMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher, CachedMaxCUSearcher, ClassitMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher, CobwebMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher, MaxCategoryUtilitySearcherDecorator, NoCommonRatingAttributeSkipMaxCUSearcher, SharedMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher

    public interface IMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher
extends java.io.Serializable
    Searches in a given set of nodes for a subset of nodes. A merge of all nodes in the subset results in a new node with the greatest category utility of all possible merges.
